org.gbif.nub.build

Class NubWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.nub.build.NubWriter

  • public class NubWriter
extends Object
    Tools that generate all files for a new nub build. Should be able to share this class at some point with importing routines when we get there. The files generated are ready to be quickly inserted into teh clb database.
